public abstract static class ShadowSmsManager.MultimediaMessageParams extends Object
Base class for testable parameters from calls to either ShadowSmsManager.downloadMultimediaMessage(android.content.Context, java.lang.String, android.net.Uri, android.os.Bundle, android.app.PendingIntent) or ShadowSmsManager.downloadMultimediaMessage(android.content.Context, java.lang.String, android.net.Uri, android.os.Bundle, android.app.PendingIntent).
